trans-unit.source: Handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName> event to receive notification when the new document finishes loading.
trans-unit.target: Hantera den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName>händelsen för att få ett meddelande när det nya dokumentet har lästs in.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs object passed to the event handler lets you retrieve the location of the new document through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs.Url%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs objekt skickades till de händelsehanterare kan du hämta platsen för det nya dokumentet via den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs.Url%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs.Url%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName> event occurs, the new document is fully loaded, which means you can access its contents through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: När den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName>händelse inträffar nytt dokument laddas fullständigt, vilket innebär att du kan komma åt innehållet via den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName>
